<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (mhmạ kạn ạlḥạl hạtqdr .. yạlly btsẖq ạlbḥwr
 mhmạ kạn ʿ ạlạ̉rḍ ḍlmẗ .. ạlsmạ mlyạnẗ nwr)2
 zy mạ jạlk nḥmyạ .. bạlbkạ wnạdy̱ ʿlyk
 klnạ jạyyn bnṣrkẖ .. yạ yswʿ md ạ̹ydyk
 ạlqrạr- bạrk blạdy .. bạrk blạdy
 yạ sạmʿ ạlṣlạẗ fy qlwb kl ạlbsẖr
 bạrk blạdy .. bạrk blạdy
 ạ̹ltft lṣrạkẖ qlwbnạ .. wạrsl lynạ ạlmṭr
 2- (rwḥk ạlqdws yjmʿ .. ạlʿẓạm mn kl wạdy
 tḥyạ tnṭq tnḥny lk .. tʿtrf bạsmk yạ fạdy)2
 fy ạlṣlyb bạṭrḥ dẖnwby .. dẖnb ậbạỷy wwlạdy
 yạ rḥym ạlqlb ạgẖfr .. wạstmʿ lậhạt blạdy
 3- fy ạlkẖyạm yʿly̱ htạfnạ .. nrfʿ ạlʿlm ạlsmạwy
 ạlrb byjhz nfwsnạ .. wạlʿdw jrạbh kẖạwy
 ynhḍ ạlnạym wysmʿ .. ạlndạ ạ̹ntm sẖhwdy
 wklnạ mn qlb wạḥd .. nṭlbk bạrk blạdy</lyrics>
<title>mhmạ kạn ạlḥạl</title>
</song>